      "date": "2014-11-05 18:27:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nBob - No fault of yours, but these patch-to-a-patch things are impossible to read.  Did you have to make any modifications to the patch, or were you able to just drop it right in?  If so, I'll give it a +1 on that basis.",
