        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-11-05 18:32:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPatrick, it came very close to just dropping the changed lines 1-for-1 into the sles version of the patch.  Did it by working on the patched fs/ext4 source file & then refreshing the patch with quilt, but the effect was quite the same.\n\nIMHO the best review method might be actually applying the revised patch series and then looking carefully at the resulting ldiskfs source.  That's probably what I would do.  I'm very much hoping for thorough review from ext4/ldiskfs experts.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
